<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .nav-link {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Contrast Security Agent Information</h1>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
            <a href="/" class="nav-link">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
        </div>

        <div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h2>üõ°Ô∏è Contrast Flex Agent Status</h2>
            <p>The Contrast Flex Agent provides real-time application security monitoring for this Node.js application.</p>
            
            <h3>Agent Capabilities:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Runtime Application Self-Protection (RASP)</strong> - Real-time attack blocking</li>
                <li><strong>Interactive Application Security Testing (IAST)</strong> - Vulnerability discovery during testing</li>
                <li><strong>Software Composition Analysis (SCA)</strong> - Open source vulnerability detection</li>
                <li><strong>Application Security Monitoring</strong> - Continuous security visibility</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h3>üîç Security Monitoring</h3>
            <p>This application is being monitored for the following security events:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>SQL Injection attempts</li>
                <li>Cross-Site Scripting (XSS)</li>
                <li>Path Traversal attacks</li>
                <li>Command Injection attempts</li>
                <li>SSRF (Server-Side Request Forgery)</li>
                <li>Insecure Direct Object References</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h3>üìä Agent Configuration</h3>
            <p>Current Contrast Agent settings:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Agent Type:</strong> Node.js Flex Agent</li>
                <li><strong>Version:</strong> 4.5.0</li>
                <li><strong>Mode:</strong> Assess + Inventory</li>
                <li><strong>TeamServer:</strong> <span id="teamserver-url">Loading...</span></li>
                <li><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #4CAF50;">Active</span></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="background: rgba(0, 150, 136, 0.2); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h3>üöÄ Getting Started</h3>
            <p>To maximize security insights:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Exercise the vulnerable endpoints on the home page</li>
                <li>Check the TeamServer for vulnerability reports</li>
                <li>Review attack events and blocked requests</li>
                <li>Analyze the security findings in your Contrast dashboard</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
            <a href="/contrast" class="nav-link">View Raw Agent Data</a>
            <a href="https://docs.contrastsecurity.com" target="_blank" class="nav-link">Documentation</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Load TeamServer URL dynamically
        fetch('/contrast')
            .then(response => response.json())
            .then(data => {
                document.getElementById('teamserver-url').textContent = data.teamserver;
            })
            .catch(error => {
                document.getElementById('teamserver-url').textContent = 'Not configured';
            });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
